addProxy

void addProxy(URI jid,
              InetSocketAddress address)
Adds a proxy for the given JabberID at the given address. If the address isn't given, we will attempt to do a NAT Traversal to find an address for the given Jabber ID.

Parameters:
jid - Jabber ID for the peer
address - (optional) address at which we expect the proxy to be listening
